{"type": "article", "id": 13257, "title": "刀叉勺三位一体", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-10T08:03:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702101223y6DTPrujV07kzMX4.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>英国设计工作室 Map Studio 为百货公司 Fortnum &amp; Mason 设计了一款特殊的餐具，把刀，叉和勺子三种功能结合在一起。其灵感来自一战时期士兵们使用的一种类似的工具，设计初衷是方便人们外带食物时使用方便，叉子用于搅拌沙拉，勺子适合吃甜品，而锯齿刀可以进行简单的切割和搅拌，而不会伤到嘴。他们表示多种功能合为一体，可以减少二氧化碳量。产品由塑料和不锈钢两种材料可以选择。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261408403Fgjcsf0tA7vp1nZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140840jTszrblK8Bc23qDx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261408412jCA9NiJnoU5z6pm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140841irajB62X9JkbYmve.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261408413EdmaT6i8ZOlfwt9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140842sYjBbgmav9MrGqLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140843gYcbP73HA5sSfX4O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140843eWl76URuOLhBDHwE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261408434Broh6vMcVESiaJK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}